P0.3 IAM Task Execution Role Implementation Notes:

Files modified:
- go.mod, go.sum: Added github.com/aws/aws-sdk-go-v2/service/iam v1.53.6
- internal/state/types.go: Added ResourceExecutionRole constant
- internal/providers/aws.go: Added IAM role provisioning and cleanup

Key functions added:
1. provisionExecutionRole(ctx, cfg, infra, tags) - Creates IAM role with:
   - ECS tasks assume-role policy
   - AmazonECSTaskExecutionRolePolicy attached
   - Role name: agent-deploy-ecs-task-{infra_id} (max 64 chars)
   - Role ARN stored in infra.Resources[ResourceExecutionRole]

2. deleteExecutionRole(ctx, cfg, infra) - Cleanup that:
   - Detaches managed policy first
   - Deletes the IAM role
   - Handles NoSuchEntity gracefully

3. mapToIAMTags(tags) - Helper to convert map to IAM tag format

Changes to existing code:
- createInfra: Calls provisionExecutionRole before provisionLogGroup
- createTaskDefinition: Uses execution role ARN from infra.Resources (was nil)
- teardown: Calls deleteExecutionRole after deleteLogGroup

Security impact:
- ECS tasks now have proper least-privilege permissions
- Role is tagged for tracking and cleanup
